<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.5.10">
<l>ceṅkama lakkaḻalil ciṟṟitaḻ pōlviraliṟ</l>
<l rend="indent">cērtika ḻāḻikaḷum kiṇkiṇi yumaraiyiṟ</l>
<l>taṅkiya poṉvaṭamum tāḷanaṉ mātaḷaiyiṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">pūvoṭu poṉmaṇiyum mōtira mumkiṟiyum</l>
<l>maṅkala vaimpaṭaiyum tōḷvaḷai yumkuḻaiyum</l>
<l rend="indent">makaramum vāḷikaḷum cuṭṭiyu mottilaka</l>
<l>veṅkaḷ kuṭikkaracē yāṭuka ceṅkīrai</l>
<l rend="indent">yēḻula kummuṭaiyā yāṭuka vāṭukavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that the shining rings joined to [your] fingers like small petals</l>
<l rend="indent">and the tinkling anklets to [your] red lotus feet,</l>
<l>the gold cord that abides on [your] waist, the gold and sapphire</l>
<l rend="indent">with flowers of the good pomegranate on [your] legs,</l>
<l>the finger-ring, the coral bracelet, the auspicious five weapons,</l>
<l rend="indent">the arm band, earring, Makara, ear-studs, and forehead ornament,</l>
<l>shine suitably, O King of our family, please dance!</l>
<l rend="indent">You who possesses the seven worlds, dance the Ceṅkīrai, please dance!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
